<h2>MomentaArt's 2014 Spring Benefit and Raffle</h2>

<div class="text_content">

  <p>Thank you for supporting Momenta Art through your work. Though we are fortunate to be supported by a number of governmental organizations and private foundations, a significant portion of our operation relies on fundraising events. We truly appreciate your support for making our continued operation possible.</p>

  <p><strong>Preview Exhibition:</strong> April 18 - May 8, 2014</p>
  <p><strong>Preview Party:</strong> Friday, April 18, 7-9pm</p>
  <p><strong>Raffle drawing and party:</strong> Thursday, May 8, 7-10PM</p>

