  <h4>Practical Information</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>We are primarily looking for framed two-dimensional works or sculptures. In case of paper-based two-dimensional works, please ensure that it is framed.</li>
    <li>Due to space restrictions please limit your donation to wall pieces no larger than 18 inches in any dimension and sculptural pieces <strong>no larger than 18 inches in any dimension.</strong></li>
    <li>Please restrict your donation to works valued <strong>under $1000.</strong></li>
    <li>The collection of over 100 artworks is a big undertaking, so it will be greatly appreciated if work can be <strong>dropped off at Momenta (56 Bogart St) Thursday, March 13th, through Monday, March 24th, Thursday through Monday between noon and 6pm.</strong> If you will be unable to get your work to the gallery during this time, please call or email the gallery to make other arrangements.</li>
  </ul>
  
  <h4>Online Submission of Image and information of your work</h4>

  <p>In order to make the process easy, one of our supporters, <a href="http://www.artcat.com/" target="_blank">ArtCat</a>, has generously created an online submission form. Please <%= link_to 'submit', guidelines_path %> the following information of your work by March 24th.</p>

   <ul>
    <li>A jpeg image (maximum side ranging between 600 -1000 pixels, 72 dpi)</li>
    <li>Your name</li>
    <li>Title of the work</li>
    <li>Year </li>
    <li>Size</li>
    <li>Medium</li>
    <li>Edition (if applicable)</li>
    <li>Estimated value</li>
    <li>"Courtesy of" credit(can be "courtesy of the artist"). </li>
  </ul>


  <p>Thank you so much for your kind cooperation. We look forward meeting seeing you at the events.</p>

  <p>Best regards,</p>

